    "body": "to add on that, \r\nwe set the env var of the process that's currently running and since all test are executed in the same process they share the same env values, so there's no isolation.\r\n\r\nbut since all tests are run in parallel with no deterministic order I wonder if we should just isolate on a per-test basis like:\r\n\r\n```\r\nset_vars: HashMap<String, String>\r\n```\r\n\r\nbut if this is now on a per-test basis this is essentially the same as a test internal solidity var so I think this is a won't fix\r\n",
